@startuml UC-05
title UC-05 - Cancelar Reserva

autonumber
actor FuncionarioRececao
participant ReservaController
participant IReservaService
participant ReservaRepository
participant AuditoriaOperacaoService

FuncionarioRececao -> ReservaController : POST /reservas/{id}/cancelar
ReservaController -> IReservaService : cancelar(id)
IReservaService -> ReservaRepository : findWithDetalhesById(id)

alt reserva inexistente ou nao cancelavel
  ReservaRepository --> IReservaService : vazio ou estado invalido
  IReservaService --> ReservaController : erro
  ReservaController --> FuncionarioRececao : mostrar mensagem de erro
else reserva ATIVA
  ReservaRepository --> IReservaService : Reserva
  IReservaService -> IReservaService : setEstado(CANCELADA)
  IReservaService -> ReservaRepository : save(reserva)
  IReservaService -> AuditoriaOperacaoService : registarSucesso(CANCELAR_RESERVA)
  IReservaService --> ReservaController : Reserva cancelada
  ReservaController --> FuncionarioRececao : confirmar cancelamento
end

@enduml
